<TEI xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" xmlns:frus="http://history.state.gov/frus/ns/1.0"><text><body><div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1948-04-22T17:00:00-05:00" frus:doc-dateTime-min="1948-04-22T17:00:00-05:00" n="689" subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d689">
                    <note rend="inline" type="source">846G.79693/4–1548: Telegram</note>
                    <head><hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Acting Secretary of State</gloss>
                            to the Ambassador in China</hi> (<persName type="to"><hi rend="italic">Stuart</hi></persName>)</head>
                    <opener>
                        <dateline rendition="#right"><placeName><hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi></placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1948-04-22T17:00:00-05:00">April 22, 1948—5
                            p.m.</date></dateline>
                    </opener>
                    <p>613. Embs assumption correct reurtel 678 Apr 15, particularly in view last
                        para urtel 608 Apr 5. Repeated Shanghai as 734.</p>
                    <closer><signed><hi rend="smallcaps">Lovett</hi></signed></closer>
                </div>
